latestIgtvVideos.caption:

Perfect time to think about your skin and hair along with your health 🤷‍♀️

So I have this homemade veggie face mask with goodness of oil and honey, which will make your skin,

Let's do the drill🤟.
1️⃣ CLEANSE:
- very important to clean your face properly.
2️⃣ SCRUB:
- @forestessentials hand pounded organic fruit. 
3️⃣ MASKING:
- veggie pulp made with Tomato, bottle gound, beet, carrot, amla and a little mint. - Add @blackandgreenproducts avocado oil spray. - Add @organicindiaofficial organic honey wild forest. - mix well 🤷‍♀️
4️⃣ SKIN ROUTINE:
- @facespabysanakhan double power vitamin c serum. - @facespabysanakhan hyaluronic serum. - @clinique moisture surge.
